#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.90"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.90:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.90:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga"
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.90:0.3"
msgid "90. Dutiyasekhasutta"
msgstr "90. A Trainee (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "“These five things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an5.90:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.90:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu bahukicco hoti bahukaraṇīyo viyatto "
"kiṅkaraṇīyesu;"
msgstr ""
"Firstly, a mendicant trainee has many duties and responsibilities, and is "
"competent in many tasks."

msgctxt "an5.90:1.4"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:1.5"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the first thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu appamattakena kammena divasaṃ "
"atināmeti;"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant trainee spends their day doing trivial work."

msgctxt "an5.90:2.2"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the second thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.117"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu saṃsaṭṭho viharati "
"gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee mixes closely with laypeople and "
"renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson."

msgctxt "an5.90:3.2"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:3.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the third thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu akālena gāmaṃ pavisati, atidivā "
"paṭikkamati;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee enters the town at the wrong time, and "
"returns too late in the day."

msgctxt "an5.90:4.2"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:4.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

# Note that BB has “gets to hear”, but sotum is not in the text. katha is often not just passive listening but engaging in conversation.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu yāyaṃ kathā ābhisallekhikā "
"cetovivaraṇasappāyā, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t get to take part in talk about self-"
"effacement that helps open the heart, when they want, without trouble or "
"difficulty. That is,"

#. VAR: akicchalābhī na akasiralābhī → kicchalābhī kasiralābhī (bj, s1-3, km pī)
msgctxt "an5.90:5.2"
msgid ""
"appicchakathā santuṭṭhikathā pavivekakathā asaṃsaggakathā vīriyārambhakathā "
"sīlakathā samādhikathā paññākathā vimuttikathā vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, "
"evarūpiyā kathāya na nikāmalābhī hoti na akicchalābhī na akasiralābhī;"
msgstr ""
"talk about fewness of wishes, contentment, seclusion, keeping your distance, "
"arousing energy, ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and "
"vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an5.90:5.3"
msgid "riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, nānuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They neglect retreat, and are not committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:5.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fifth thing that leads to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an5.90:5.5"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno parihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "These five things lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:6.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "These five things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an5.90:6.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.90:6.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na bahukicco hoti na bahukaraṇīyo viyatto "
"kiṅkaraṇīyesu;"
msgstr ""
"Firstly, a mendicant trainee doesn’t have many duties and responsibilities, "
"even though they are competent in many tasks."

msgctxt "an5.90:6.4"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:6.5"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the first thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant "
"trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na appamattakena kammena divasaṃ "
"atināmeti;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t spend their day doing trivial work."

msgctxt "an5.90:7.2"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:7.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the second thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant "
"trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.118"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:8.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu asaṃsaṭṭho viharati "
"gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t mix closely with laypeople and "
"renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson."

msgctxt "an5.90:8.2"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:8.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the third thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant "
"trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:9.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu na atikālena gāmaṃ pavisati, nātidivā "
"paṭikkamati;"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee doesn’t enter the village too early or "
"return too late in the day."

msgctxt "an5.90:9.2"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:9.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth thing that doesn’t lead to the decline of a mendicant "
"trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:10.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sekho bhikkhu yāyaṃ kathā ābhisallekhikā "
"cetovivaraṇasappāyā, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant trainee gets to take part in talk about self-"
"effacement that helps open the heart, when they want, without trouble or "
"difficulty. That is,"

msgctxt "an5.90:10.2"
msgid ""
"appicchakathā santuṭṭhikathā pavivekakathā asaṃsaggakathā vīriyārambhakathā "
"sīlakathā samādhikathā paññākathā vimuttikathā vimuttiñāṇadassanakathā, "
"evarūpiyā kathāya nikāmalābhī hoti akicchalābhī akasiralābhī;"
msgstr ""
"talk about fewness of wishes, contentment, seclusion, keeping your distance, "
"arousing energy, ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and "
"vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an5.90:10.3"
msgid "na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, anuyuñjati ajjhattaṃ cetosamathaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t neglect retreat, and are committed to internal serenity of heart."

msgctxt "an5.90:10.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo dhammo sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"This is the fifth thing that doesn't lead to the decline of a mendicant "
"trainee."

msgctxt "an5.90:10.5"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā sekhassa bhikkhuno aparihānāya "
"saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr "These five things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.90:10.6"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.90:10.7"
msgid "Theravaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.1"
msgid "Rajanīyo vītarāgo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.2"
msgid "kuhakāssaddhaakkhamā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.3"
msgid "Paṭisambhidā ca sīlena,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.90:11.4"
msgid "thero sekhā pare duveti."
msgstr ""
